{"tid":2225990,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"月夕行動 多謝搞手","createTime":"2020-10-01T17:19:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T14:13:42.000Z","uid":6845,"like":5,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"30512857241f587279430f43cb337a6239ba46a4","tid":2225990,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T17:19:19.000Z","msg":"去到呢一刻 我諗大部份人都明咩事<br />\n雖然fail 得好嚴重 計劃亦都有漏洞<br />\n但人手先係最大問題 同樣嘅計劃放喺上年可能已經好唔同 <br />\n<br />\n除左搞手問題 <br />\n手足平時對cctv擺位情況夠唔夠了解 體格都好重要<br />\n<br />\n同埋月夕行動完全擺脫和理非遊行被動劣勢，係一場主動行為，之後可以做幾多嘢，<span class=\"red\">視乎有幾多人相信</span><br />\n<br />\n當然 同樣嘅嘢做第二次效果一定會打折<br />\n但計劃一日未完全曝光一日都仲有機會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n辛苦每一個等咗好耐嘅手足<br />\n多謝搞手精心策劃<br />\n不完美可改善<br />\n<br />\n不如大家諗下如果有一日有機會光復香港<br />\n會唔會願意喺戰爭中犧牲<br />\n<br />\nSUCK : 我死都唔會解散<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2086311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2086311</a><br />\n<br />\n【長文】其實月夕行動好反映到我地目前嘅抗爭陰<br />\n暗面<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2225941\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2225941</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d7c51df4d2f5c9ae70d79027d1c27236948d7b18","tid":2225990,"uid":314462,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T17:19:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4278e0e0224fe88db29a2e5519fd522192461e59","tid":2225990,"uid":143343,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T17:20:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"425d3caaf4e87fbbb305efa975657d0288986a61","tid":2225990,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T17:52:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/pigkiss/9325\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fpigkiss%2F9325&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w19MQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=9ab86bc3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/pigkiss/9325</a><br />\n<br />\n試完知道唔得咪得<br />\n手足堆船出左海 係船長自己汁生架啦<br />\n大風大浪 人腳唔齊，咪下次先再嚟過<br />\n<br />\n其實個方法好似係ok, 理想化得嚟<br />\n好似未柒撚到唔可行<br />\n當佢係香城online EX beta版<br />\n封測唔夠人玩，咪再招下人先"},{"pid":"32465dea8d302bf10812d6be90d03045c23f9d54","tid":2225990,"uid":319935,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T18:40:50.000Z","msg":"巴打你係咪唔方便解釋 定係你真係國安<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b651f1d5c68976197223b44d74c976ef324604e","tid":2225990,"uid":6845,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"32465dea8d302bf10812d6be90d03045c23f9d54","tid":2225990,"uid":319935,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T18:40:50.000Z","msg":"巴打你係咪唔方便解釋 定係你真係國安<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T20:24:37.000Z","msg":"呢個世界會唔會有 有良心嘅強姦犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有從來唔做壞事唔分化既國安<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1ab81b0525e6d742b9fa200d72aaabf4e9c643f","tid":2225990,"uid":319935,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8b651f1d5c68976197223b44d74c976ef324604e","tid":2225990,"uid":6845,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"32465dea8d302bf10812d6be90d03045c23f9d54","tid":2225990,"uid":319935,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T18:40:50.000Z","msg":"巴打你係咪唔方便解釋 定係你真係國安<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T20:24:37.000Z","msg":"呢個世界會唔會有 有良心嘅強姦犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有從來唔做壞事唔分化既國安<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T20:39:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝你嘅答覆"},{"pid":"baea542c99939dac687492141d0b0eea28328cfe","tid":2225990,"uid":208260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b651f1d5c68976197223b44d74c976ef32